query:
INSERT INTO workout_scoring_feedback (workout_data_id, user_id, effort_rating)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
        ON CONFLICT (workout_data_id, user_id)
        DO UPDATE SET
            effort_rating = $3,
            created_at = NOW()
        RETURNING
            id,
            workout_data_id,
            user_id,
            effort_rating,
            created_at
